### Fetch All Tasks
GET http://localhost:3200/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

### Create A Tasks
POST http://localhost:3200/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
{
    "title": "Test Task Title",
    "date": "2023-11-28T12:00:00Z",
    "description": "Test task details",
    "priority": "normal",
    "status": "completed"
}

### Update A Task
PUT http://localhost:3200/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
{
    "id": "5cdb1158-182e-402a-966f-d58e308554cc",
    "status": "todo"
}